..TEXT:
Perhaps an allusion to "what the Spirit saith unto
the churches," ^Revelation~ ii. 7: "To him that overcometh will I
give to eat of the tree of life, which is in the midst of the
paradise of God."  And also the "hidden manna," and the "morning
star," and the "white raiment," and the name not blotted "out of
the book of life."
